About Me
I am Jennifer Roush, aka n!, and I have done many different things in my life — driven tractor-trailers across the USA, authored and published books, done data analysis. I am a mother, a gamer, an app developer, a marksman. I am Autistic.
What I have never done is conform to what anyone expected me to be. And I think that's the magic of existence.
Whether you are Autistic with ADHD like me, or simply overwhelmed by the circumstances of life, my goal in this stage of my own life is to bring you revolutionary love and care in teeny-tiny embodied moments. So I built things: no-conflict text role-playing games with somatic grounding exercises built in, micro-meditations, and games that don't pressure you.
